foia:ProcessedAppealSection.foia:FootnoteText: Appeals of denials of information based on exemption or other reason. All of the Department’s appeals in this category are processed through the Appeals Review Panel; therefore, this statistic includes appeals for the Office of Inspector General. This statistic covers the entire fiscal year reporting period. Also included are appeals of denial of requests for expedited processing and appeals of denial of requests for fee waivers. These are covered only by the time period from July 1, 2008 to September 30, 2008.
